{"tid":859136,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"愛港之聲：包二奶嘅人先會學普通話","createTime":"2018-10-12T09:48:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T08:42:00.000Z","uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c849bc43a770973f05b0f4cbeced878036dfda9b","tid":859136,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T09:48:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20150102/18988761\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150102%2F18988761&d=SOIlvL8gMyq5cs67G5zfIwIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=a6ee14af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150102%2F18988761&h=756444c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20150102/18988761</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上次接受鳳凰衞視訪問時，愛港之聲召集人高達斌突然澳門崔世安上身，用騎呢普通話回應記者提問，經《蘋果動新聞》報道後，即被逾十萬網民嘲笑。噚日佢接受《蘋果》訪問時，即刻第一時間主動同記者講：「你哋係《蘋果》吓嘛？我唔使用普通話講吖嘛？哈哈哈！」，自稱唔介意被網民嘲笑，更認為事件有助澄清佢無如外界流傳咁「收中央錢做事」，「我啲普通話咁渣，人哋（中央官員）都聽唔明我講乜嘢啦！」<br />\n高達斌其後更指，「包小三」嘅人先會學普通話，所以自己一定無「包小三」啦，講完自己都即刻笑，又話自己嘅英文程度都係同普通話咁上下。<br />\n八方見識過高達斌嘅「崔世安式」普通話後，唔只相信佢無包小三，仲覺得佢嘅普通話同英文口語程度，可能都未及小三喎。"},{"pid":"e9499141fd655bba496c1bcf9d1c91be92837c81","tid":859136,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T09:50:31.000Z","msg":"姐係笑支那人都係二奶, 反了反了"},{"pid":"22785e298f7b157b2274ecd3cc3eb3cc6743d5b7","tid":859136,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T09:51:23.000Z","msg":"咁又講得岩<br />\n<br />\n好多香港人都成日笑鳩人普通話講得差<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1d0666df774c9139fbee70d4d8cc0dacd5bdb4f","tid":859136,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T08:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}